@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@
+# Smee component
+
+The Smee component deploys [gosmee][gs] in server mode to the host cluster.
+
+This allows our clusters to provide a webhook forwarding service similar to
+[smee.io][sm].
+
+[gs]: https://github.com/chmouel/gosmee
+[sm]: https://smee.io/
